## Distributed Erlang configuration
## Node naming is handled by env.sh.eex

## Use native DNS resolver (getaddrinfo) instead of Erlang's built-in inet_res
## Required for Fly Managed Postgres .flympg.net domains on Fly.io
## Erlang's inet_res can't resolve Fly's internal DNS, but the OS resolver can
-kernel inet_native_dns true
